{"tid":1043711,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰鎚online]EU私服","createTime":"2019-03-02T12:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T07:06:41.000Z","uid":136776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f113bcf07c335ead3691316e47b2ec4443441c8b","tid":1043711,"uid":136776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:47:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.returnofreckoning.com/about.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.returnofreckoning.com%2Fabout.php&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=d7e46677\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.returnofreckoning.com/about.php</a><br />\n<br />\n近排搵到呢隻好耐之前玩過既mmorpg, 戰鎚online 既私服<br />\n有冇人記得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻game 主打PVP, 基本上你lv 1就可以沖入戰場打陣形戰<br />\n最緊要係私服人數就長期維持 700+ 基本上T4 日日都開片<br />\n新手T1 入到去都日日打哂交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係HK連EU ping值應該係150~250不等, 但玩了幾日我覺得冇咩大影響 <br />\n打過一場 50+ RVR 都冇咩點lag 應該都玩到落去<br />\n最緊要係免費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有興趣既巴打絲可以玩下<br />\n下面係小小介紹影片<br />\n<br />\n職業介紹<br />\n陣形分為order同destruction, 雙方分別有3個種族<br />\n<br />\nOrder<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UJZoIoTVn5U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUJZoIoTVn5U&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=639a82fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UJZoIoTVn5U</a><br />\n<br />\nDestruction<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dn9QpTK66E0&amp;t=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDn9QpTK66E0%26t%3D&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=c8aa242b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dn9QpTK66E0&amp;t=</a><br />\n<br />\n利伸: 岩岩玩了幾日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f3a42f921b6a78649bbdd4d77a0c3bea2a6106","tid":1043711,"uid":136776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:50:39.000Z","msg":"有興趣既巴打我地可以 開個DISCORD<br />\n因為我都係岩岩玩番 好多野都學緊<br />\n都係跟住D人on99 咁去殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想玩既基本上都係註冊完DOWLOAD 就入到<br />\n官網有教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.returnofreckoning.com/join.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.returnofreckoning.com%2Fjoin.php&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=eb69176d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.returnofreckoning.com/join.php</a>"},{"pid":"9ca2f384ffadda88b85efac2adedc0c875f89d47","tid":1043711,"uid":136776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"感覺隻GAME 仲未見到有亞洲人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a75a5572a5c3c19f662a5d6cabe515d9ae573c","tid":1043711,"uid":136776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"私服都營運了幾年 <br />\n雖然唔收錢但係營運個班友都有KEEP<br />\n住更新 例如果d class balance 同fix bug<br />\n基本上個community 都知大家係死忠 <br />\n所以都幾helpful<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbf99469cd78fdf123628f983e2f4ad67b5978a","tid":1043711,"uid":136776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34604b26dd88d015dfe3b9335373ff1e2dd114b","tid":1043711,"uid":136776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T13:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.